{"tid":1321690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家警察係咪見到唔順超就可以拉？","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:47:31.000Z","uid":236646,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"263c9e470cbc573677eda3a089c7e40fe64257d6","tid":1321690,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"旺角單野好誇張，人地無帶口罩拎手機影下警察，你警察就可以隨意禁住人然後抄人地書包？再搵幾條罪告人地？？？以後見到警察真係調頭走...仲惡過黑社會。香港人仲有冇人權呀？條街以後警察行晒啦....不如直頭宵禁啦。以後唔比香港人行街消費，你警察行晒佢啦....<br />\n<br />\n原本正係對班防暴同埋管理示威個班反感。<br />\n原來成街巡邏個班都係咁樣執法。<br />\n以後見到警察真係調頭走....咁樣執法啤下佢容乜易又比佢拉番警署砌你幾條罪....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea1ad81c1830c0627625891b8efccc6a78dd977","tid":1321690,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"63cae50ef4544a5c738c5c75a674eed5bda438fc","tid":1321690,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民